Margaret's story will leave you speechless...


"I never thought I'd be the person sharing a transformation story, but what happened to me is simply too extraordinary to keep quiet.


Six months ago, I experienced what I can only describe as the most devastating moment of my adult life – at my own daughter's wedding.


The photographer was arranging family photos when he looked at me, then at my daughter, with visible confusion. 'I'm sorry, ma'am,' he said loudly enough for everyone to hear, 'I need the MOTHER of the bride in this shot, not the grandmother.'


The entire wedding party fell silent. My daughter squeezed my hand as tears welled in my eyes. 'She IS my mother,' my daughter whispered.


The photographer apologized profusely, but the damage was already done. I spent my daughter's entire wedding hiding from cameras and fighting back tears in the bathroom.


That night in my hotel room, I forced myself to really look in the mirror under the harsh bathroom lights. What I saw horrified me. Every deep line, fold, and wrinkle seemed magnified. The stress of caring for my sick husband, working 60-hour weeks, and going through menopause had ravaged my appearance without me even realizing it.


The deep ‘11 lines’ between my brows made me look perpetually angry. The hollow shadows under my eyes gave me a permanently exhausted look. The deep folds around my mouth had carved my face into an old woman’s mask. And the sagging along my jawline had completely erased the face I remembered.


I looked DECADES older than my 52 years – and a stranger had just confirmed my worst fear in front of everyone I love.


For weeks after the wedding, I couldn’t bear to look at a single photo. I consulted THREE plastic surgeons who all recommended the same thing: a full facelift, neck lift, brow lift, and injectable fillers – with a heart-stopping price tag of R427,500 and SIX WEEKS of painful recovery.


As a working woman who had just helped pay for a wedding, this was impossible. I was seriously considering a second mortgage on my home when my daughter’s college roommate called me with something that would change my life forever.

They're calling it living collagen that activates fresh when you mix it,' she told me. The before and after photos from our lab tests are STAGGERING.


I was deeply skeptical.


After 30 years of broken promises from beauty products and hundreds of dollars wasted on creams that did nothing, I had zero expectations. But what did I have to lose?


That night, I opened the freeze-dried collagen sphere and mixed it with the activator serum - watching it dissolve into the freshest treatment I'd ever seen.


I applied the living BioEdge™ collagen to my clean face at 10:30 PM and went to bed, completely unaware that my life was about to change forever.


The next morning, I stumbled to the bathroom half-asleep and flipped on the light. What happened next is burned into my memory forever.


I SCREAMED so loudly my husband came running.


The face staring back at me in the mirror was NOT the same face I'd gone to bed with.

THE TRANSFORMATION WAS SHOCKING AND IMMEDIATE.

The deep furrows between my brows had VIRTUALLY DISAPPEARED.


The hollow 'tear troughs' that aged me so severely were PLUMPED AND FILLED.


The 'marionette lines' that dragged my mouth downward had DRAMATICALLY SMOOTHED.


My skin looked FIRMER with a LUMINOSITY I hadn't seen in 15+ years.


I touched my face in disbelief – there was an ACTUAL STRUCTURAL CHANGE in how my skin felt beneath my fingertips. It was like the living collagen had actually rebuilt something from within.


My husband stood frozen in the doorway, his mouth literally hanging open. 'Margaret... what on earth did you DO?' he whispered in shock.


For the first time in years, I found myself SMILING at my reflection instead of turning away from it.

NEEDLE FREE BOTOX EFFECT FROM HOME

BioEdge™'s living collagen penetrates the skin barrier to rebuild structural foundation while the proprietary Peptide Renewal Complex™ (including Argireline and bioactive tri-peptides) targets the neuromuscular pathways, instantly relaxing facial muscles that cause expression lines.


This dual-action approach delivers both immediate muscle relaxation AND long-term structural repair - something Botox injections cannot accomplish because they only address muscle movement, not skin rebuilding.


The formula works precisely where Botox clinics charge premium prices - in the ultra-sensitive areas around the eyes, between brows, and along the upper lip where repeated injections become expensive and risky.

3.

BLOCKS WRINKLE FORMATION

The average woman uses 62 facial muscles thousands of times daily, deepening expression lines with each movement.

BioEdge™'s fresh-activated peptides BLOCK the neurotransmitters responsible for these micro-contractions, preventing new wrinkles while erasing existing ones.


This creates both IMMEDIATE smoothing and LONG-TERM prevention - something even R14,400 monthly Botox treatments cannot accomplish because they wear off and require endless re-injections.

4.

REBUILDS YOUTHFUL SKIN, RESTORES FIRMNESS & ELASTICITY - ALL NATURALLY, WHILE YOU SLEEP

After age 30, collagen production declines by 1% each year — leading to visible sagging, fine lines, and skin thinning. BioEdge™'s living collagen penetrates to the dermal matrix where it triggers your own collagen synthesis, increasing skin density and structural integrity by up to 141% after just one application.


The result? Dramatically plumper, firmer skin with restored youthful volume - effectively turning back the clock 15-20 YEARS on your appearance.

Cookies

A cookie is a small amount of information that’s downloaded to your computer or device when you visit our Site. We use a number of different cookies, including functional, performance, advertising, and social media or content cookies. Cookies make your browsing experience better by allowing the website to remember your actions and preferences (such as login and region selection). This means you don’t have to re-enter this information each time you return to the site or browse from one page to another. Cookies also provide information on how people use the website, for instance whether it’s their first time visiting or if they are a frequent visitor.

The length of time that a cookie remains on your computer or mobile device depends on whether it is a “persistent” or “session” cookie. Session cookies last until you stop browsing and persistent cookies last until they expire or are deleted. WANT TO KNOW MORE ABOUT OUR SHIPPING TIMES?

Here at BioEdge™ we strive to give our customers the best experience possible as we believe that is the most important thing for any online-based company. 

Our shipping can generally be separated into two parts:


PROCESSING TIME: 

Our processing time includes order verification, product tailoring, quality check, and packaging. Processing starts within 12 hours of placing your order.


SHIPPING TIME:

The shipping time refers to the time your order takes from being shipped out to being delivered to your doorstep. 


Orders will be shipped from our international warehouses depending on which is closest to your residency. However, if our national warehouse is out of stock, your order will be shipped from one of the other warehouses. 


Due to the global pandemic, shipping times may vary depending on where in the world you are ordering from and the current state of the freight lines. 


Our shipping times are averaged from our last 5,000 orders, so we can provide our customers with the most accurate and transparent shipping information we can. 


All orders will receive tracking numbers with live updates on your package. All tracking information will be sent 12-24 hours, you can track your order here.


NOTE: If you are ordering from an island state/country, shipping times may be delayed due to shipping constraints. Shipping times exclude clearance/customs delays as these are out of our control.
